This paper primarily focuses on the security of robots, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). It also discusses the complex landscape of security in robotics, which involves cross-disciplinary perspectives, making it relevant to the sub-category of Cybersecurity (cs.CR) and Software Engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the importance of internal and external communication security, which is relevant to the sub-category of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
